        <h1>How We're Different</h1>
        <p class="col-md-11">Other weight loss plans have you focus on buzzwords that seem complex and sophisticated.  They have you eat only very specific foods (or worse, only food they provide).  They make you eat only at very specific times of day. They promise you can eat all of a certain kind of food as long as you avoid others. This is not our philosophy.</p>
