        <h3>Working with your consultant</h3>
        <p class="lead col-md-12">At the first session, your consultant will ask you what your challenges are, and help you identify challenges you didn't recognize were there.  Your consultant will listen to your long term goals, and help you develop short-term goals that bring you to your long term goals quickly and safely, while considering and addressing the challenges you face.  Then, your consultant will offer you multiple plans to achieve these short term goals.  You select what you like, and then your consultant collaborates with you to tailor it perfectly to your needs.  Nearing the end of the program, your consultant coaches you to give you the tools necessary to create and achieve your goals.  If you would like to continue the program longer than 3 months, that option is also available by letting your consultant know.</p>
